Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:10.68,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:37.18,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:40.52,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make an old man get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:48.71,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Creation Magic: \NPrison of the Fallen King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.61,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to get away anymore, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who we're facing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:59.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,we, the Black Bulls, will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.08,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:03.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:12.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Creation Magic: Swift White Hawk\Nand Wind Blade Shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:14.38,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Simultaneous spell activation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:19.26,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It will be the Golden Dawn that \Nreaches the treasure chamber first!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:26.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:39.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.41,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke just keeps getting thicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.70,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're going to suffocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:48.08,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. We have to \Nhurry up and defeat that mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.43,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can pretty much tell \Nwhere he is with my magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:56.41,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,but he'll probably dodge, even if I attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:00.34,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on our battle so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.27,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,he's able to travel at high \Nspeed within the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:07.77,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And his ability to sense magic is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.01,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,If we're to land a hit on him,\Nwe'll have to surprise him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:14.82,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we do that without \Nhim noticing our magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:23.29,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can sense your magic just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.87,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:35.29,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a barrage. Are you getting desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.21,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,That's not going to hit me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.84,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,or get rid of the smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.88,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I think the difference in our \Nexperience levels is starting to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.35,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've fought far \Nmore mages than you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.14,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.90,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I guess teamwork really is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:24.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:29.01,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:33.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:38.11,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.50,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:44.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.88,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:52.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:56.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.76,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:05.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:11.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:18.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:22.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:25.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.50,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.87,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:47.89,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that to a \Ndefenseless old man like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.97,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Man... It's definitely broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.06,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure he got some of my ribs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.98,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:09.33,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are some oddballs \Nin the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.58,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,A boy with no magic \Nwho wields a giant sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:19.61,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I can safely say that even I've never met \Nsomeone with no magic on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.47,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to end up a prisoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:27.91,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I'll diâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.48,italics,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Or just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.87,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:03.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Creation Magic: Hustling Lazy Car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.09,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Caught up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.81,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,are way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to finish him off,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.36,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,but I know we have more \Nimportant things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:39.25,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry to the treasure chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You really have the nerve to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.29,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,What is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:07:00.10,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's someone \Neven stronger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.64,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.58,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the treasure chamber is \Nthe least of our worries right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.59,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.95,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm pretty sure Mars \Nwill take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.99,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:18.50,sign_10406_87_Diamond_Kingdom_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Diamond Kingdom Mage Warrior\N{\fs30}Mars
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:18.50,top,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Diamond Kingdom's \Nsecret weapon, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.62,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Such ominous magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:32.80,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's at full strength, \Nand even he stands no chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.11,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Those stones embedded in his forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.81,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:47.47,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor that the Diamond \NKingdom is raising mage warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.21,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,with artificially amplified magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:55.21,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They choose young children \Nwith powerful magical abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.24,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,put them in fierce competition \Nwith each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.72,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,embed magical items that amplify \Ntheir powers into their bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.60,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, they have them \Nfight one another to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:11.61,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The last survivor of that death match...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.27,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,is him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:21.89,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who the opponent is... \NIs this really acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.14,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:26.15,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.13,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.53,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I let my comrade get hurt so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.13,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being protected by my \Nsubordinate, who's a peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.99,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:43.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:47.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Fierce Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.67,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.60,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Whaâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.32,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,A mineral clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.56,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:17.86,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic has no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.43,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.00,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.05,flashbackitalics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.43,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this training,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.56,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.14,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:09.64,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quitting until I hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.11,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.56,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:21.91,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.91,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.91,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.91,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:27.66,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.46,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...going to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.58,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Stop your useless attemptsâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.67,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:43.93,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.93,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.71,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pale guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:40.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pale guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:33.27,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable... and I thought \NI finally repaid my debt to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:37.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I finally catch up with you, and look at you!\NWhat the hell are you doing, Yuno?! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could get your ass kicked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.55,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I almost had him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You're all beat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You were about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.96,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to unleash \Na ferocious counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.17,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're always like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.88,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to get in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.75,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can take this guy down first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:21.48,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:26.76,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Golden Dawn, didn't stand a \Nchance against his magic, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:31.45,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,That peasant from the Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.21,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.20,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.15,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.63,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The one who made trouble at \Nthe Entrance Exam by beating
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.52,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,his opponent far worse than necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.01,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Luck the Cheery Berserker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.49,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This was the other member of \Nthe Black Bulls that was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.99,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How could I end up being \Nsaved by the Black Bulls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.96,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:09.38,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you said, I'm a bit slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.70,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:13.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.73,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who beat up the Golden Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.53,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,What if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:36.66,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will perish,\N and only the strong will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.51,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,That's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.09,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He summoned so many at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:49.09,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason for the weak \Nto stand on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:53.09,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to break people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:02.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and try to break me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.11,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.29,italics,All,0000,0000,0000,,He's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.30,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:15.75,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be the one to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.81,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.87,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How could a peasant that I can't feel \Na shred of mana from do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:39.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,All you've been doing is whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Negating magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.54,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's Asta's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Negating magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:52.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,How can he have a power\Nso unfit for a peasant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.80,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So he just got lucky and \Nended up with this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:18:00.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch him, and you'll \Nfind out if it's just luck or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on! Are you \Nfinished already, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.81,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.33,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.02,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:13.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm someone who was born without any magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.80,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have any magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.17,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,So it really was just luckâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:23.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I'm going to \Nbecome the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to prove that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:34.49,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on with his body? \NHow much has he trained?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:40.11,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King? Does he truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:48.82,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.77,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.00,italics,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.38,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:03.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King protects everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:07.64,flashbackitalics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,We were born to protect \Neveryone in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:12.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm going to lose \Nto someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.23,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:20.74,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, pebble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I may be just a pebble,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:30.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,a pebble that shatters diamonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.26,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:22.82,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't give up,\Nyou'll get there eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:02.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.63,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:12.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:18.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:20.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:23.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:26.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:32.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:37.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:39.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:42.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:44.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:48.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:54.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
