Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:12.58,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:16.79,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Treasure Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:15.91,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure Chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:19.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! So this is the treasure chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:22.79,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's any \Ntreasure worthy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:26.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just randomly open \Nstuff up and see what's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:28.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair doing it all yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:29.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Open sesameâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's no treasure chamber.\NIt's an organ chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:36.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:41.99,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,This old man's exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:45.36,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how much more abuse \NI can take from home and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.19,0:23:49.55,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 18: "Memories of You."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:55.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 18\N\N{\fs18}Memories of You
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:53.61,main,Lotus,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the rest to the young'uns \Nis this old man's magic.
